<div class="jumbotron text-center">
   <h1>Welcome to Study Buddy</h1>
   <%= link_to "FIND CLASSES", "#", class: "btn-trans", role: "button" %>
   <%= link_to "FIND ASSIGNMENTS", assignments_path, class: "btn-trans", role: "button" %>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <h1>Want people to study with?</h1>
      <p>Study Buddy is a great way to find assignments or classes you need help with. <%= link_to "Looking for a particular assignment?", assignments_path %> <%= link_to "Looking for a particular class?", "#"%> If you can't find the assignment or class you're looking for, <%= link_to "post it yourself!", new_assignment_path %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr>
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h1>How it works</h1>
      <p><strong>It's simple!</strong> <%= link_to "Sign up", signup_path %> for an account then post an assignment you want a study buddy for.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h1>Who can use it?</h1>
      <p><strong>Anyone!</strong> You don't even need to be an IU student, you just need to <%= link_to "sign up", signup_path %> for a free account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
